<pc>，</pc>
<measure quantity="9" unit="people">
<num value="9">九</num>人</measure>死於獄<pc>，</pc>扶奏申釋之<pc>。</pc>詔切責鹽鐵<pc>、</pc>度支<num value="2">二</num>使<pc>，</pc>天下監院償逋系<measure quantity="3" unit="years">
